#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"On a daily basis, house keeping tasks are created depending on the current "
"stays and assigned to employees that have house keeping shifts."
msgstr ""

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "On a resource to block line, click, drag and drop to create a slot."
msgstr ""
"Lukitaksesi resurssin rivin, luo paikka klikkaamalla, raahaamalla ja "
"pudottamalla."

